title: Winamp 5.66 (Latest) full & lite
description:
Winamp.com and associated web services will no longer be available past December 20, 2013. Additionally, Winamp Media players will no longer be available for download. Please download the latest version before that date. See release notes for latest improvements to this last release.
Thanks for supporting the Winamp community for over 15 years.


As always Winamp and Winamp Pro also feature...

        Now Playing: Artist Songs, Videos, Radio & Photos
        iPod Support: Play and manage music on your iPod
        SHOUTcast Radio and TV
        AOL Radio powered by CBS Radio
        Album Art: View Album Art

        Extended Flash video support
        Auto-Tag: Automatically update your song info
        Replay Gain: Play all your songs at a consistent volume level
        Format Converter: Transcode music to a more friendly format
